     <article>
      <div class="comment by-lol-no" id="c6690210"> 
       <p class="commentcredit"><span class="commenter">lol no.</span> • <a href="https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2015/02/everyone_wants_.html#c6690210">February 26, 2015 9:34 AM</a> </p> 
